import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from pylab import figure, text, scatter, show
In [ ]:
## defs to get data

def get_tsne_result(basis):
    '''obtain tsne result and return as a list.
    '''
    indir = './{0}.tsne_2d.npy'.format(basis)
    return numpy.load(indir).tolist()

##### data
basis_list = ['sccdftb', '631G',]
dat_list = [get_tsne_result(basis) for basis in basis_list]

line_styles = ['-', '--', ':']
line_style_id = 0

colors = [(230,  25,  75, ),
          ( 60, 180,  75, ), 
          (  0, 130, 200, ),
          (170, 110,  40, ),
          (240,  50, 230, ),
          (255, 225,  25, ),
        ]
colors = [(float(r/255), float(g/255), float(b/255),) for r,g,b in colors]

# set up
fig, ax = plt.subplots( figsize=(13, 10), dpi=300, )

# adjust individually
# make plot sqare

# spine
ax.spines['top'].set_visible(False)
ax.spines['right'].set_visible(False)
ax.spines['bottom'].set_visible(False)
ax.spines['left'].set_visible(False)

ax.tick_params(which='both', left=False, bottom=False, labelleft=False, labelbottom=False, )
    
for j in range(0, 18):
        
    path = dat_list[0][j*50:(j+1)*50]
    x = [p[0] for p in path]
    y = [-p[1] for p in path]
        
    ls = line_styles[j//6]
    c = colors[j%6]
    lbl_id = j
    lbl_stt = 'r' if j in range(0, 6) else 't' if j in range(6, 12) else 'p'
    lbl = '{0}/{1}'.format(lbl_id, lbl_stt)
    # c = 'k'
    # if j == 1:
    #     c=colors[j%6]
    ax.plot(x, y, c=c, linestyle=ls, linewidth=1.5, marker='x', markersize=4.0, )
    
for j in range(0, 18):
        
    path = dat_list[1][j*50:(j+1)*50]
    x = [p[0]+110 for p in path]
    y = [p[1] for p in path]
        
    ls = line_styles[j//6]
    c = colors[j%6]
    lbl_id = j
    lbl_stt = 'r' if j in range(0, 6) else 't' if j in range(6, 12) else 'p'
    lbl = '{0}/{1}'.format(lbl_id, lbl_stt)
    # c = 'k'
    # if j == 1:
    #     c=colors[j%6]
    ax.plot(x, y, c=c, linestyle=ls, linewidth=1.5, marker='x', markersize=4.0, )

ax.axis('equal')
plt.show()
fig.savefig('2d_tsne.png')
